&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;/computer-science/note/theme-shoka-doc/&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;🚀快速开始&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; - &lt;a href=&#34;/computer-science/note/theme-shoka-doc/dependents/&#34;&gt;💌依赖插件&lt;/a&gt; - &lt;a href=&#34;/blog/computer-science/note/theme-shoka-doc/config/&#34;&gt;📌基本配置&lt;/a&gt; - &lt;a href=&#34;/computer-science/note/theme-shoka-doc/display/&#34;&gt;🌈界面显示&lt;/a&gt; - &lt;a href=&#34;/computer-science/note/theme-shoka-doc/special/&#34;&gt;🦄特殊功能&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
